{"data":[{"name":"86:1","price":"天と、夜訪れるものにかけて（誓う）。¹","arabic":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ وَٱلطَّارِقِ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5932,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　アッラー*によるこの誓いについては、整列者章１の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-samāi wal-ṭāriqi ","translations":["By the sky","and the night comer","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-samāi","wal-ṭāriqi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,3260],[2,3260,5165]]}},{"name":"86:2","price":"そして、夜訪れるものが何かを、何があなたに知らせるか？","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلطَّارِقُ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5933,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā adrāka mā al-ṭāriqu ","translations":["And what","can make you know","what","the night comer (is)","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","adrāka","mā","al-ṭāriqu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2160],[2,2160,3240],[3,3240,3350],[4,3350,5025]]}},{"name":"86:3","price":"（それは）穿ち煌めく星¹である。","arabic":"ٱلنَّجۡمُ ٱلثَّاقِبُ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5934,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　夜に現われ、昼には姿を隠す星が、「夜訪れるもの」と形容されている（イブン・カスィール８：３７４参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"al-najmu al-thāqibu ","translations":["(It is) the star","the piercing","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["al-najmu","al-thāqibu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1960],[2,1960,3575]]}},{"name":"86:4","price":"いかなる者でも、その上に見守る者（天使*）¹がついていない者はない。","arabic":"إِن كُلُّ نَفۡسٖ لَّمَّا عَلَيۡهَا حَافِظٞ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5935,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　この天使*たちについては、雷鳴章１１の訳注も参照（前掲書８：３７５参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"in kullu nafsin lammā ʿalayhā ḥāfiẓun ","translations":["Not","(is) every","soul","but","over it","(is) a protector","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["in","kullu","nafsin","lammā","ʿalayhā","ḥāfiẓun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,900],[2,900,1730],[3,1730,2480],[4,2480,4350],[5,4350,5430],[6,5430,6875]]}},{"name":"86:5","price":"では人間に、自分が何から創られたのか、考えさせてみよ。","arabic":"فَلۡيَنظُرِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مِمَّ خُلِقَ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5936,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"falyanẓuri al-insānu mimma khuliqa ","translations":["So let see","man","from what","he is created","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["falyanẓuri","al-insānu","mimma","khuliqa",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2140],[2,2140,4160],[3,4160,5680],[4,5680,6905]]}},{"name":"86:6","price":"彼は、射出する液体¹から創られたのだ。","arabic":"خُلِقَ مِن مَّآءٖ دَافِقٖ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5937,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「射出する液体」とは、子宮に射出される精液のこと（ムヤッサル５９１頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"khuliqa min māin dāfiqin ","translations":["He is created","from","a water","ejected","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["khuliqa","min","māin","dāfiqin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,710],[2,710,980],[3,980,4820],[4,4820,6045]]}},{"name":"86:7","price":"後背部と、胸部の間から分泌される（、液体から）。¹","arabic":"يَخۡرُجُ مِنۢ بَيۡنِ ٱلصُّلۡبِ وَٱلتَّرَآئِبِ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5938,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「後背部と胸部」には、「男性の精液が、そこで分泌される」「男性の精液が後背部で女性の精液が胸部で分泌される」という解釈（アッ＝サアディー９１９頁参照）のほか、「前者が男性、後者が女性を表している」という説もある（アル＝カースィミー１７：６１２４参照）。また、人間の創造の変遷については、巡礼*章５、信仰者たち章１４も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"yakhruju min bayni al-ṣul'bi wal-tarāibi ","translations":["Coming forth","from","between","the backbone","and the ribs","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["yakhruju","min","bayni","al-ṣul'bi","wal-tarāibi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,910],[2,910,1990],[3,1990,2670],[4,2670,3570],[5,3570,7365]]}},{"name":"86:8","price":"本当にかれ（アッラー*）は、彼を（その死後に、生きた状態へと）戻すことがお出来のお方。¹","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ عَلَىٰ رَجۡعِهِۦ لَقَادِرٞ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5939,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　関連するアーヤ*として、ビザンチン章２７も参照（イブン・カスィール８：３７５参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"innahu ʿalā rajʿihi laqādirun ","translations":["Indeed, He","to","return him","(is) Able","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["innahu","ʿalā","rajʿihi","laqādirun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1850],[2,1850,2590],[3,2590,3710],[4,3710,5275]]}},{"name":"86:9","price":"秘められたことが試される（、復活の）日*に。¹","arabic":"يَوۡمَ تُبۡلَى ٱلسَّرَآئِرُ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5940,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　その日、善悪の別なく、人が隠していた全ての物事と、心に秘めた信仰心と不信仰が露（あら）わ になる（アル＝クルトゥビー２０：８参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma tub'lā al-sarāiru ","translations":["(The) Day","will be tested","the secrets","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma","tub'lā","al-sarāiru",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,560],[2,560,1270],[3,1270,4445]]}},{"name":"86:10","price":"ならば、後には、（自分自身からアッラー*の懲罰を押しのける、）いかなる力も援助者もない。","arabic":"فَمَا لَهُۥ مِن قُوَّةٖ وَلَا نَاصِرٖ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5941,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"famā lahu min quwwatin walā nāṣirin ","translations":["Then not","(is) for him","any","power","and not","any helper","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["famā","lahu","min","quwwatin","walā","nāṣirin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,590],[2,590,1210],[3,1210,2560],[4,2560,4300],[5,4300,4890],[6,4890,6385]]}},{"name":"86:11","price":"回帰するもの¹を有する、天にかけて、","arabic":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ ذَاتِ ٱلرَّجۡعِ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5942,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「回帰するもの」の解釈には、「（降っては止むのを繰（く）り返す、あるいは海から水を湛（たた）えて 大地に戻って来る）雨」「（出現しては姿を隠す）天体」「（人間の行いと共に、天へと戻って行く）天使*」などといった諸説がある（アッ＝シャウカーニー５：５６０－５６１参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-samāi dhāti al-rajʿi ","translations":["By the sky","which","returns","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-samāi","dhāti","al-rajʿi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2680],[2,2680,3300],[3,3300,4725]]}},{"name":"86:12","price":"また、（植物を生えさせるべく、）亀裂を有する大地にかけて（誓う）、¹","arabic":"وَٱلۡأَرۡضِ ذَاتِ ٱلصَّدۡعِ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5943,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　同様のアーヤ*として、眉をひそめた章２６も参照。また、アッラー*によるこの誓いについては、整列者章１の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-arḍi dhāti al-ṣadʿi ","translations":["And the earth","which","cracks open","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-arḍi","dhāti","al-ṣadʿi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1130],[2,1130,1730],[3,1730,3085]]}},{"name":"86:13","price":"本当にそれ（クルアーン*）は、（真理と虚偽を）裁断する御言葉であり、","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ لَقَوۡلٞ فَصۡلٞ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5944,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"innahu laqawlun faṣlun ","translations":["Indeed, it","(is) surely a Word","decisive","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["innahu","laqawlun","faṣlun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1820],[2,1820,3720],[3,3720,4655]]}},{"name":"86:14","price":"戯言ではない。","arabic":"وَمَا هُوَ بِٱلۡهَزۡلِ","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5945,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā huwa bil-hazli ","translations":["And not","it","(is) for amusement","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","huwa","bil-hazli",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,670],[2,670,1080],[3,1080,2185]]}},{"name":"86:15","price":"本当に彼ら（使徒*とクルアーン*を噓呼ばわりする者たち）は、（真理を退けるための）策略を講じている。","arabic":"إِنَّهُمۡ يَكِيدُونَ كَيۡدٗا","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5946,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"innahum yakīdūna kaydan ","translations":["Indeed, they","are plotting","a plot","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["innahum","yakīdūna","kaydan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1850],[2,1850,3230],[3,3230,4255]]}},{"name":"86:16","price":"われも策略¹を講じるのだが。","arabic":"وَأَكِيدُ كَيۡدٗا","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5947,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　この「策略」とは、かれらが知らない所から、徐々に破滅（はめつ）へと導いて行くこと（アル＝バガウィー５：２４０参照）。その具体例については、家畜章４４を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-akīdu kaydan ","translations":["But I am planning","a plan","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-akīdu","kaydan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1170],[2,1170,2235]]}},{"name":"86:17","price":"ならば（使徒*よ）、（懲罰が下ることを急がずに、）不信仰者*に猶予を与えよ。彼らに暫し、猶予を与えるのだ。","arabic":"فَمَهِّلِ ٱلۡكَٰفِرِينَ أَمۡهِلۡهُمۡ رُوَيۡدَۢا","category":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq"],"ayahNumber":5948,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"famahhili al-kāfirīna amhil'hum ruwaydan ","translations":["So give respite","(to) the disbelievers","Give respite to them ","little","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["famahhili","al-kāfirīna","amhil'hum","ruwaydan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1070],[2,1070,2720],[3,2720,4210],[4,4210,6875]]}}],"chapter":["86 (At-Tariq)","At-Tariq","Surah At-Tariq","Chapter At-Tariq","Tariq","Surah Tariq","Chapter Tariq","At Tariq","Surah At Tariq","Chapter At Tariq","Surah 86","Chapter 86","The Morning Star","الطارق"],"version":{"key":"japanese_saeedsato","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ja","version":"1.0.10","last_update":1709035504,"title":"Japanese translation - Saeed Sato","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Japanese by Saeed Sato. printed in 1440 H."}}